<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">The Bottom Line</h2>
<p class="text-navy-400 leading-relaxed"><strong>AI isn't magic. It's infrastructure.</strong></p>
<p class="text-navy-400 leading-relaxed">The companies seeing results treat AI like electricity—not a gadget.</p>
<ul class="space-y-3 text-navy-400"><li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-gold-500 mr-3">•</span><span>They don't celebrate using it</span></li><li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-gold-500 mr-3">•</span><span>They celebrate what it enables</span></li><li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-gold-500 mr-3">•</span><span>They build systems around it</span></li><li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-gold-500 mr-3">•</span><span>They measure outcomes obsessively</span></li></ul>
